Install Dependencies
pip install gradio requests


Set Up Your Hugging Face API Token
Replace the placeholder token in headers = {"Authorization": "Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"} with your Hugging Face token.
You can get your token from https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens.

Run the App
python app.py


Access the Interface
The app will automatically launch in your browser or give you a public shareable link.

